As the 3 warriors walk due.

Dark steps out shadows "Hello Little brother."

Liono jumps back and drawn his sword. 

Dark looks "I'm not here to fight I want to go with you there no use in space 
for defeated villains and I want to see with my own eyes what make you so 
powerful.

Rynn looks at dark "Make that I we." As a another bot steps out of the 
shadows and puts her arm around dark.

Dark returns the gesture "My lady let head out."

Liono put his sword away "Come on brother let get this show on the road."

As the 5 warriors walk down the path to the east.
